name: Booking a service with >24h duration - client's place

steps.name: Input search text and press Enter
$("app-search form input") set value("Regional Marketing Producer (gg5tf1utq)")
Verify that the search result is correct
$("app-search-result ion-card-content app-service-link") should have(text "Regional Marketing Producer (gg5tf1utq)")
Verify that the service data is correct
$("app-service-widget") should have(text "I'm more than just a hammer. In a hole in the ground there lived a hobbit.")

parameters.name: serviceDescription
parameters.value: I'm more than just a hammer. In a hole in the ground there lived a hobbit.

steps.name: $("app-service-widget/app-service-location") should have([text "Russia", text "Moscow", text "Apt. 566 767 Ashly Fields, North Dominiquetown, KY 97696"])

parameters.name: ServiceAddress
parameters.value: Apt. 566 767 Ashly Fields, North Dominiquetown, KY 97696

steps.name: $("app-service-widget") should have(text "Ordering of this service will be approved automatically")
$("app-book div.calendar/with text: 11") should have([css class "selected", 10 s.])
$("app-confirmation-step div.footer ion-button") should not have([css class "button-disabled", 10 s.])
$("app-confirmation-step div.footer ion-button") should not be([visible, 10 s.])
Click to see sent order details
$("app-sent-order-page app-sent-order div.order-full-info__more-info a") should be([visible, 10 s.])
